## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="72dad-135">当在设计时和运行时添加序列时，会自动将其分配给 "默认" <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> 对象， <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> 如果 "默认" 不存在，则自动将其分配给第一个可用的图表区。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72dad-135">When a series is added at both design time and run time, it is automatically assigned to the "Default" <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> object, or the first available chart area in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> if "Default" does not exist.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="72dad-136">如果不想绘制序列，请将此属性设置为长度为零的字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72dad-136">Set this property to a zero-length string if you do not want the series to be plotted.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
' Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
Public Sub CreateSecondLegend()  
    ' Attach the first series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
    ' Attach the second series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
End Sub 'CreateSecondLegend  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
public void CreateSecondLegend()  
{  
     // Attach the first series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
     // Attach the second series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="72dad-220">获取或设置序列的阴影颜色，它可以是任何有效的 ARGB (alpha、红色、绿色、蓝色) 值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72dad-220">Gets or sets the shadow color of a series, which can be to any valid ARGB (alpha, red, green, blue) value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="72dad-221">Alpha 值可用于实现逼真的阴影效果;尝试为阴影使用颜色值 "128，0，0，0"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72dad-221">The alpha value can be used to achieve a realistic shadow effect; try using a color value of "128,0,0,0" for shadows.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="72dad-222">若要实现阴影，请将 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> 属性设置为非零值 (0) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72dad-222">To implement a shadow, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> property to a value other than zero (0).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
' Set series shadow color and offset  
Public Sub SetSeriesShadow()  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowOffset = 2  
End Sub 'SetSeriesShadow  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Set series shadow color and offset   
public void SetSeriesShadow()  
{      
    Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue;  
    Chart1.Series["Default"].ShadowOffset = 2;  
}  
```
